data.description: MOVE IN READY!  The beautiful Avondale model is spacious & has been completely upgraded throughout. This open concept home offers 3 spacious bedrooms, plus a flex room, 2 full bath,  2 car garage, vinyl flooring in common areas, carpet in all bedrooms and vaulted ceilings throughout. The thoughtfully designed gourmet kitchen features custom wood cabinets, island complimented with quartz countertops and farmhouse sink, breakfast bar, and stainless-steel appliances. Spacious walk-in closets and sizable master bath with double vanities makes the master retreat the perfect place to unwind and relax. The large windows throughout allow an ample amount of natural light. Tohoqua a master planned community, features a grand 20+ acres of green space and parks for the ultimate indoor/outdoor lifestyle. The community also gives the opportunity to enjoy tennis courts, gym, clubhouse and a gorgeous resort style pool. Great location within minutes to shops, restaurants, and all major highways.
